  "text": "A number of recent studies, however, have suggested that eddies do not contribute to the offshore heat balance of the SEP. [CITATION_1] , using a GCM, found that the net incoming solar heat flux of 18 W m 22 was nearly fully balanced by the gyre circulation of upwelled cold water from the coast. Colas et al.",
